author: Ben Baby
title: Churchill stops Lee for big district win
text:
Photo: Tom Reel / San Antonio Express-News Image 1 of / 1 1 Charger quarterback Devin Faktor slashes through the middle as Churchill plays Lee at Heroes Stadium on October 10, 2015.
Photo: Tom Reel / San Antonio Express-News Charger quarterback Devin Faktor slashes through the middle as... Churchill stops Lee for big district win 1 / 1 Back to Gallery There were enough subplots to sustain the drama between Lee and Churchill on Saturday night, but the biggest plotline is the one that will be important in a few weeks.
Churchill dropped back-to-back contests coming into its district game against the Volunteers. Lee, on the other hand, picked up a critical district win last week before Saturday’s game with potential playoff implications.
Churchill made sure the game wasn’t as dramatic as the narrative surrounding it. The Chargers won 45-18 at Heroes Stadium to snap a two-game slide.
